    <h4 class="text-info">Nalban Boating Complex</h4>
    <p>
        Located At The Heart Of Salt Lake City, Just 12 Kms. Away From Central Kolkata. It Is A Beautiful Leisure Spot For Families Who Would Like To Spend Few Hours In A Placid Lake.
    </p>
    <p>
        One Can Enjoy An Exclusive Boating Tour On One Of The Many Boats Available Such As Paddle Boats, Hovercraft Or Deluxe Shikara. The Main Attraction Of This Place Is The Four Hundred Acre Picturesque Lake Which One Can Explore. If You Really Want To Spend A Special Day Out With Your Family Amidst Nature, Nalban Boating Complex Is An Ideal And Automatic Choice In The City Today.
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Mirik</h4>
    <p>
        Mirik, A Nest In The Hills Is One Of The Most Famous Hill Resorts In West Bengal. The 1.25 Km "Long Lake" Is Fed By Perennial Streams. A Floating Fountain In The Middle Of The Lake Is A Joy Forever And Very Often, You May Find The Glory Of Kanchenjunga Reflected In The Lake Waters. A Rich Forest With Thousands Of Trees Clothes The Slopes On The West. A 3.5 Km Zigzag Foot Walk Takes You Along The Lake – A Sleek Footbridge Connects The Garden On The East With The Woods On The West. Alone Or With Company, You Are Sure To Enjoy A Boat-Ride In The Lake.
    </p>
